CREATE TABLE [dbo].[send_created]
(
    id varchar(50) NOT NULL,
    [date] varchar(50) NOT NULL,
    user_id varchar(50) NULL,
    organization_id varchar(50) NULL,
    send_type varchar(5) NULL,
    has_password varchar(5) NULL,
    max_access_count int NULL,
    last_modified_date datetime2(7) NOT NULL
)
WITH
(
    DISTRIBUTION = HASH (user_id),
    CLUSTERED INDEX (id)
)
GO

CREATE INDEX user_id_ix ON dbo.send_created (user_id)
GO

CREATE INDEX last_modified_date_ix ON dbo.send_created (last_modified_date)
GO
